Package: tidyedgar
Title: Tidy Fundamental Financial Data from S.E.C.'s EDGAR API
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Gerard", "Gimenez-Adsuar", , "gerard@solucionsdedades.cat", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = ""))
Description: Automates the retrieval and formatting of fundamental financial data from the SEC's Electronic Data Gathering, Analysis, and Retrieval system (EDGAR) API. It streamlines the process of accessing complex financial information, transforming it into a tidy, analysis-ready format.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
